<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>547</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ a wǒ kěn qiè de qiú gào nǐ, shī ēn gěi zhōng guó jiào huì,
 nǐ tīng lái zì yuǎn shān de hū huàn, gěi zhōng guó kāi yī tiáo lù ba!
 bié ràng bǎi xìng rào dào xíng zǒu, dì xiōng pī zhe mián yáng de pí dào chù bēn pǎo,
 zhǔ a wǒ kěn qiè de qiú gào nǐ, shī ēn gěi zhōng guó jiào huì,
 zuò zài zì jǐ de pú táo shù xià, yě hē pú táo zhī niàng de jiǔ,
 xiàng tiān kōng yī yàng méi yǒu zhà lán, fú yīn zài dà de chàng tōng.</lyrics>
<title>méi yǒu zhà lán de tiān kōng 迦南547</title>
</song>